# Kitchen example

home "Kitchen" unit cm

room Kitchen at 0,0 size 330x250 label "Kitchen"

window Kitchen south at 70 size 150
door Kitchen north at 115 size 82 swing inward

item counter in Kitchen at 20,25 size 70x190 label "Counter"
item sink in Kitchen at 110,25 size 80x55 label "Sink"
item table in Kitchen at 180,105 size 110x80 label "Table"

note Kitchen "Keep sink path clear"
